    TelaTale <

    /h1> <
    ul >

    li >

    Link to = '!#' > Stories < /Link> <
    /li> <
    li >
    <
    Link to = '!#' > Writers < /Link> <
    /li> <
    li >

    Link to = '!#' > About < /Link> <
    /li> <
    li >

    /li> <
    /ul> <
    /nav>
  );
};
export default Navbar;
